      "date": "2013-09-28 15:31:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWhat about having mount (or mount.lustre in the shorter term) look up the journal device in userspace and supply the \"-o journal_device\" mount option to the kernel?\n\nAlternately, could you send this patch to Linux-ext4 and get some feedback if this is something they would accept upstream?",
