      "date": "2013-09-29 07:45:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/908c4c74-28d3-11e3-ac84-52540035b04c).  Ran 16 tests.  No failures.",
